{"tid":798642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被封「最性感富豪」 她擁數十億資產","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T13:09:19.000Z","uid":149494,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"04e187f99d48e44526146cc673f8ce9da85c5028","tid":798642,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"財經中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n有「大陸最性感女富豪」之稱的李穎，年輕時的求學、職涯都相當順遂，更可以用「開外掛」來形容，30歲時還被阿里巴巴集團主席馬雲親自登門拜訪，共同創立了雲鋒基金。時至今日，年僅38歲的李穎已坐擁數億人民幣的資產，而她的座駕還是價值約3600萬台幣的勞斯萊斯。<br />\n<br />\n根據《中國雪花新聞》報導，1980年出生的李穎求學生涯相當順遂，優異的她，僅僅花了3年時間，就獲得美國麻省理工的計算機科學學士、經濟學學士和電子工程及計算機科學碩士。畢業後待過麥肯錫、Ikanos、UT和KPCB等頂尖公司，更僅花了13年時間就從職員爬上KPCB合夥人的角色，若換做是別人，很可能花30年都辦不到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2010年時，馬雲看中李穎各方面的資源及能力，親自到美國矽谷向她遊說，希望她能夠成為合夥人。最終李穎便成為雲鋒基金最早的3位創辦人之一，靠著她強大的工作能力，替雲鋒基金拉攏多位大陸商界大老投資，首期規模就來到100億人民幣（約450億台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n現今李穎所掌管的基金規模來到幾百億人民幣，她個人身家也是要用億級人民幣來計算，而她的座駕還是勞斯萊斯經典款「幻影」，一台要價約3600萬台幣。李穎儘管有如此傲人的成就，卻在媒體面前卻非常低調，只期許自己能夠更加努力。（編輯：林緯平）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.bangqu.com/r2/news/20171223/3048794e476b65497458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.bangqu.com%2Fr2%2Fnews%2F20171223%2F3048794e476b65497458.jpg&h=0931e20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkpic.crntt.com/upload/201711/21/104885965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkpic.crntt.com%2Fupload%2F201711%2F21%2F104885965.jpg&h=7a9e6215&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b4dac88291e29e1b07155bb9aca3a100557ea","tid":798642,"uid":50740,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"支那雞"},{"pid":"daf9e78f94d26754fde63bdd4d35462e348b87da","tid":798642,"uid":4964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"邊度性感?"},{"pid":"1c098b173b310a7f7fc424cee793f9047a105bbe","tid":798642,"uid":66943,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/4a/20090113131213_10d2fe49ac10f29bdc5b21ff0c0afcc1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20090114042103\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F4a%2F20090113131213_10d2fe49ac10f29bdc5b21ff0c0afcc1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20090114042103&h=d55b156a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e79aadaf5b243c6a57f381412c13660e1703a9","tid":798642,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"嚇死,仲以為係甘比..."},{"pid":"6d619da29f16687119442abc2b1d14032cba489b","tid":798642,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"47f6de5f568e4a8910318595667bf6b0bf235c61","tid":798642,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"換係男人有冇咁既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c116021125c8e163d440daac67b525e8563228","tid":798642,"uid":67551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"正常樣<br />\n<br />\n但白手興家而正常樣嘅少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca439d38ffa6eee4f48bc09f88f89e1898a35730","tid":798642,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0c116021125c8e163d440daac67b525e8563228","tid":798642,"uid":67551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"正常樣<br />\n<br />\n但白手興家而正常樣嘅少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"你點解可以咁天真"},{"pid":"aab2fa1b46589cad20b4649ec9ca3a6e93e97b77","tid":798642,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ca439d38ffa6eee4f48bc09f88f89e1898a35730","tid":798642,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0c116021125c8e163d440daac67b525e8563228","tid":798642,"uid":67551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018